Fixes:
flickering cards

Code improvements:

Deseable:
Add to game settings list of enable events and cards, so players can customize their experience



Events:
Blood Price — attacking costs HP
Cowardice — warriors can't attack unless outnumbered

Cards:
Medal of Honor — reward card for achieving kills
War Stories — draw extra cards based on kills this turn
Veteran's Blade — weapon that gets stronger with kills
Tribute — enemy must pay gold or lose a warrior
Grudge — bonus damage against the player who last killed your warrior

Systems:
Warrior Ranks (Blooded / Veteran / Elite) — warriors gain rank through kills, unlocking passive bonuses
End-Game Stats — post-game summary screen (kills, damage dealt, etc.)